00:00:18.439 --> 00:00:21.439
Willie, they were planning to do a single
cut and just drop the whole tree.

00:00:21.439 --> 00:00:25.400
-[Willie West] Yeah the homeowner claimed that's what
she was going to try and do. The problem

00:00:25.400 --> 00:00:29.150
with that Curtis, is this tree is about
30% dead. And the majority of the

00:00:29.150 --> 00:00:31.480
Deadwood is over on the street side.

